reviewText: Again, this series continues on a path of excellent action, adventure and humor as the cast  brings the Major Crimes Dept front and center in the effort to protect and serve.  OUTSTANDING!!!!!
I'm so happy that this finally became available.  There were a couple of glitches in the background music, but the show itself was fine.  I do wish there were closed captions.
Very disappointed to discover that 3 of the 6 discs won't play/pixelate on all media players and as the set was bought more than 30 days ago, I can't get a replacement.
glad it was released. only issue is that the background music is distorted sometimes.
Was so glad it came in time for a binge watch!  Great quality considering its age.
